Package: options
Title: Utilities and improvements for working with R's global options mechanisms
Version: 0.2
Date: 2015-02-17
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Brown", , "chris.brown@decisionpatterns.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides intuitive interface and seamless, dropin replacements for
    R's global option mechanism that allows for easy inspection, retrieval and
    setting of options, e.g. getOptions( foo$bar[['baz']] ) does the right
    thing.
url: URL: https://github.com/decisionpatterns/options
BugReports: https://github.com/decisionpatterns/options/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
